 <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Study Guide · Updated April 2026</span>
 <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-1 mb-4">Best English Learning Apps for Kids: Top 5 Apps Compared</h1>
 <p class="text-lg text-slate-400">Fun, safe, and effective apps to help your child learn English from ages 2 to 12.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-green-950/60 border border-green-700 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
 <p class="font-bold mb-2">Quick Verdict</p>
 <p class="text-slate-300"><strong>Best overall:</strong> Lingokids. Ages 2-8, gamified learning, affordable</p>
 <p class="text-slate-300"><strong>Best for older kids:</strong> Duolingo Kids. Ages 6-12, structured curriculum</p>
 <p class="text-slate-300"><strong>Best free option:</strong> Khan Academy Kids. All ages, completely free</p>
 </div>

 <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Children learn languages naturally when they're having fun. The right app can make English learning feel like play, not homework. But not all apps are created equal. Some are just games with English words. Others teach real skills.</p>
 <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">We tested the most popular kids' English learning apps. Here's what works.</p>


    <!-- Table of Contents -->
